import React from "react"; const Privacy = () => { return (

Privacy Policy

Last Updated: December 30, 2024

This Privacy Policy (the “Policy”) describes how Student with Benefits (operating as SWB, “we”, “us”, or “our”) collects, uses, and discloses your personal information.

This Policy applies to personal information related to:

  • Users: Individuals who are registered users or subscribers to the Student with Benefits App.
  • Non-Users:
    • Individuals who receive offers, deals, or other promotions (the "Offers") from or through the Student with Benefits App.
    • Individuals who receive communications about the services we offer (the “Communications”) as a result of referrals from Users.
    • Individuals who visit our websites, social media pages, or communicate with us.
  • Partners: Businesses, institutions, or organizations offering deals and promotions via the Student with Benefits App.
  • Employees and Applicants: Individuals working with us or interested in applying for a role at Student with Benefits.
  • Service Providers: Entities contracted to provide technical, marketing, or operational support for Student with Benefits.

If you fall into any of the categories above, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to the terms of this Policy.

I. Definitions

  • Student with Benefits Account: Your account on the Student with Benefits App.
  • Student with Benefits App: The mobile application providing deals, offers, and promotions to university students and eligible users.
  • Partners: Businesses or organizations offering promotions via the Student with Benefits App.
  • You: Any individual falling into one of the categories mentioned above.

II. Information We Collect and Use

A. Users

1. Information We Collect:

  • Full name
  • Email address
  • Date of birth
  • University name (if applicable)
  • Phone number
  • Username and password for your account
  • Location data (if enabled on your device)
  • Technical information (e.g., IP address, device identifiers, browser details)

2. How We Use Your Information:

  • Provide the services available on the Student with Benefits App.
  • Offer personalized recommendations and updates.
  • Verify your eligibility for specific promotions or offers.
  • Analyze app usage to improve performance and features.
  • Communicate with you about account updates, offers, and promotions.

B. Non-Users

1. Information We Collect:

  • Your name and contact information.
  • Information provided to us by Users or Partners when they refer you for an offer or promotion.

2. How We Use Your Information:

  • To deliver Offers or Promotions.
  • To respond to inquiries or feedback.

C. Partners and Service Providers

1. Information We Collect:

  • Business name, contact details, and promotional information.
  • Transactional and financial details for payment processing.

2. How We Use Your Information:

  • Facilitate listing of offers on the Student with Benefits App.
  • Analyze and improve partner services.
  • Process payments and manage accounts.

D. Employees and Applicants

1. Information We Collect:

  • Full name and contact information.
  • Resumes, CVs, and employment history.
  • Identification documents (if required by law).

2. How We Use Your Information:

  • Facilitate listing of offers on the Student with Benefits App.
  • To process job applications.
  • To manage employment records.

III. Legal Basis for Processing

  • Consent: Where you explicitly consent to data collection (e.g., signing up for the app or enabling location tracking).
  • Contractual Obligations: To fulfill services or agreements made with you.
  • Legal Compliance: To adhere to applicable laws and regulations.
  • Legitimate Interests: For business purposes, such as improving our services, marketing, and maintaining operational efficiency.

IV. Data Retention

We retain personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this Policy or to comply with legal obligations. Once the retention period expires, your data will be securely deleted.

V. Data Sharing

We may share your personal information with:

  • Service Providers: For data analysis, payment processing, or marketing.
  • Partners: To provide offers and promotions.
  • Legal Authorities: If required by law or to protect the rights and safety of Student with Benefits and its users.
  • Third Parties: With your explicit consent.

VI. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information, including encryption and secure storage. However, no system is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute data protection.

VII. Your Rights

Under applicable data protection laws, you have the right to:

  • Access, correct, or delete your personal data.
  • Withdraw your consent at any time.
  • Object to the processing of your data for legitimate interests.

To exercise these rights, contact us at studentwithbenefits@gmail.com.

VIII. Cookies and Tracking Technologies

We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance user experience and collect non-personal data. You may disable cookies through your browser or device settings, though this may limit app functionality.

IX. Changes to this Policy

We may update this Policy from time to time. The latest version will be posted on the Student with Benefits App, and significant changes will be communicated to you directly.

X. Contact Us

For any questions or concerns regarding this Policy, please contact:

  • Email: studentwithbenefits@gmail.com
  • Address: Beirut, Lebanon
); }; export default Privacy;
